  "url": "https://www.lankadeepa.lk/news/\u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7-\u0dad\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4-\u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1-\u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2-\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca-\u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dae\u0db1-\u0d85\u0d82\u0d9a-\u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2/101-619184",
  "time_ut": 1662104680,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0da7 \u0dad\u0ddc\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0dd4 \u0d9c\u0db1\u0dca\u0db1 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2 \u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dbd\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd4\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dae\u0db1 \u0d85\u0d82\u0d9a \u0daf\u0dd9\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Telephone numbers are given from the President's office for people to get information",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "President's Secretary Mr. Saman Ekanayake informed all the secretaries of the ministries today that it is mandatory to provide efficient and prompt service to the people who come to the government institutions to get services.",
        "The President's Secretary also stated that since it is the primary responsibility of all ministries and government officials to work for the convenience of the public, a response program should be established in all ministries and government institutions by providing efficient service without inconveniencing any person.",
        "Several phone numbers and an email address were also introduced for the convenience of the people in getting information from the Presidential Secretariat."
      ],
